message: "Gasaway bragged about promoting the 16-year old girls on commercial sex websites, recruiting sex customers for them, and offering to protect them while they worked as child sex workers."

data.description: The Napa Special Investigations Bureau has arrested 21-year old San Bernardino resident, Travonte Gasaway Jr., in a sting operation to combat human trafficking.
data.title: Southern California man arrested for reported attempt to recruit Napa teenagers for sex trade
